{"tid":1583853,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"灣仔萬麗海景酒店有黑警今日結婚？","createTime":"2019-09-20T23:40:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T23:43:12.000Z","uid":79590,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"61e83ef57b3820f900ed3542d6bba6cdbe029608","tid":1583853,"uid":79590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T23:40:54.000Z","msg":"小弟唔係相關部門，淨係收到上頭指示，今日有黑警結婚，小心有人搞事。<br />\n有無宴會部、BC 同事check 下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n習大大當年黎香港就包左呢間酒店住，可惜當年過唔到政治審查，被逼放假，無得見習大大一面。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/79V6U3d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F79V6U3d.png&h=696dd49c&s={SIZE}\" /><div style=\"text-align: left;\"></div>"},{"pid":"a7841a51aac089bb9bc0324a862c4f84e45da3af","tid":1583853,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T23:41:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">由於都係有好多人唔明行動有咩意義同目標 於是係正式攻略之前出個簡化版</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【行動】【主線】 【922】【SUCK4.0】 【多圖】 【簡易式攻略目標 】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1583476\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1583476</a>"},{"pid":"de7e9980e3b2783888507452a7e5b7802179d5a7","tid":1583853,"uid":79590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T23:41:31.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"f8915d2b5362ed0490d3037033a02c8582dac746","tid":1583853,"uid":79590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T23:41:41.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"8c37b3490a143d2989e22716fb46ca8cb194f8b9","tid":1583853,"uid":79590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T23:41:52.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"0b772459e290810a29ca1e85322ade462399ef51","tid":1583853,"uid":79590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T23:42:02.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"72ae06626e16d5e77dbe08be1fcdad3e4ff0a158","tid":1583853,"uid":79590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re